oai_dc:dc.dc:title: RESEARCH ACTIVITIES OF THE BEACH EROSION BOARD
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Caldwell, Joseph M.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Beach Erosion Board
research priorities
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The purpose of this paper is to describe the research program of the Beach Erosion Board and to discuss the reasons which led to the establishment of this program. Introductory statements are given as to the functions of the Beach Erosion Board and the necessity of research activities to support these functions.
oai_dc:dc.dc:source: Coastal Engineering Proceedings; No. 2 (1951): Proceedings of Second Conference on Coastal Engineering, Houston, Texas, 1951.; 16
